title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Cluckin’ Bell Farm Raid
content:
To prepare for this operation, you’ll need to build a slush fund of laundered money, along with other mission-critical decisions that will determine your final advance.

Once you’ve lined everything up, you’ll need to smuggle yourself into Cluckin’ Bell’s factory farm complex and make off with the haul, boosting your own notoriety while knocking the cartel and the city’s corrupt law-enforcement officers down a few pegs in the process.
